{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-101-to-200/problem-199-iterative-circle-packing","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"project-euler-problems-101-to-200","demoType":null,"title":"Vežba 199: Zatvaranje kruga po krugu uzastopno","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Tri kruga jednakog radijusa postavljeni su unutar većeg kruga na način da svaki par krugova međusobno dodiruje, a unutrašnji krugovi se ne preklapaju. Postoje četiri nepokrivene \"prazmine\" koje će biti popunjene redom drugim dodirujućim krugovima.</p>\n<img alt=\"a diagram of non-overlapping circles\" src=\"https://cdn-media-1.freecodecamp.org/project-euler/199-circles-in-circles.gif\" style=\"background-color: white; padding: 10px; display: block; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; margin-bottom: 1.2rem;\">\n<p>Svaki ciklus, najveći mogući krug postavlja se u svaku prazninu, što stvara više praznina za sledeći ciklus. Nakon 3 ciklusa (kao što je prikazano na slici), postoji 108 praznina, a površina koja nije pokrivena krugovima iznosi 0.06790342, zaokruženo do osam decimalnih mesta.</p>\n<p>Koji deo površine nije pokriven krugovima nakon revolucija <code>n</code>? Navedite svoj odgovor zaokružujući ga na osam decimalnih mesta koristeći format x.xxxxxxxx .</p>\n</section>","id":"5900f4341000cf542c50ff46","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"Euler","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"project-euler","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":301837,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-101-to-200/problem-199-iterative-circle-packing"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function iterativeCirclePacking(n) {\n\n  return true;\n}\n\niterativeCirclePacking(10);","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>iterativeCirclePacking(10)</code> trebalo bi da vrati broj.</p>","testString":"assert.isNumber(iterativeCirclePacking(10));"},{"text":"<p><code>iterativeCirclePacking(10)</code> treba da vrati <code>0.00396087</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(iterativeCirclePacking(10), 0.00396087);"},{"text":"<p><code>iterativeCirclePacking(3)</code> treba da vrati <code>0.06790342</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(iterativeCirclePacking(3), 0.06790342);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/project-euler/#project-euler-problems-101-to-200","dashedName":"problem-199-iterative-circle-packing","certification":"project-euler","disableLoopProtectTests":true,"disableLoopProtectPreview":true,"superBlock":"project-euler","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"project-euler-problems-101-to-200","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-101-to-200/problem-200-find-the-200th-prime-proof-sqube-containing-the-contiguous-sub-string-200","prevChallengePath":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-101-to-200/problem-198-ambiguous-numbers","id":"5900f4341000cf542c50ff46","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":1,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"script","ext":"js","contents":"// solution required","history":["script.js"],"fileKey":"scriptjs"}]}},"id":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-101-to-200/problem-199-iterative-circle-packing"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}